Distribution and natural history. The new species is only known from Grabag on the south coast of Purworejo Regency, Central Java Province, Java, Indonesia (
Fig. 7
). The type locality in the South Central Java basin area is enclosed by mountain ranges to the north, west, and east, which include active volcanoes (Darman & Sidi 2000 ).
